**Specializations and Focus Areas:**

* Finance
* Marketing
* Accounting
* Analytics
* Entrepreneurship
* Healthcare Management
* Technology Management
* Global Business

**Admission Requirements:**

* Undergraduate GPA
* GMAT/GRE scores
* Work experience (typically 2-5 years)
* Letters of recommendation
* Personal statement
* TOEFL/IELTS for international students
